about.description: The Point Cloud Library (PCL) is a standalone, large scale, open project for 2D/3D image and point cloud processing.

name: pcl
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "pcl" %}
{% set version = "1.13.1" %}
{% set major_version = version.split(".")[0] %}
{% set minor_version = version.split(".")[1] %}
{% set sha256 = "8ab98a9db371d822de0859084a375a74bdc7f31c96d674147710cf4101b79621" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/pointcloudlibrary/{{ name }}/archive/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  run_exports:
    - {{ pin_subpackage('pcl', max_pin='x.x.x') }}

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - {{ cdt('mesa-libgl-devel') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('mesa-dri-drivers') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libselinux') }}        # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxdamage') }}        # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxxf86vm') }}        # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxext') }}           # [linux]
    - cmake
    - ninja                          # [win]
    - make                           # [unix]
    - pkgconfig
  host:
    - xorg-libxfixes                 # [linux]
    - flann
    - eigen
    - boost-cpp
    - qhull
    - vtk
    - libpng
    - glew
    - qt-main  # [not ppc64le]
  run:
    - flann
    - {{ pin_compatible('boost-cpp', max_pin='x.x.x') }}
    - qhull
    - vtk
    - glew
    - __osx >={{ MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET|default("10.9") }}  # [osx and x86_64]

test:
  commands:
    - test -d $PREFIX/include/{{ name }}-{{ major_version }}.{{ minor_version }}/{{ name }}              # [not win] 
    - if not exist %LIBRARY_INC%\\{{ name }}-{{ major_version }}.{{ minor_version }}\\{{ name }} exit 1  # [win] 

about:
  home: http://www.pointclouds.org
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Point Cloud Library (PCL)
  description: |
    The Point Cloud Library (PCL) is a standalone, large scale, open project for 2D/3D image and point cloud processing.
  doc_url: http://www.pointclouds.org
  dev_url: https://github.com/pointcloudlibrary/pcl

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - chambbj
    - hobu
    - Tobias-Fischer
